== Warp List State ==

Dynamically generated list of goods that selected planet accepts

  # Next Planet in Range -> WarpListState
  # Previous Planet in Range -> WarpListState
  # Buy <item> (Relative Price, Number available to Purchase) -> WarpListState
  # Warp To Planet -> InWarpState
  # Back -> OnPlanetState
